1
00:00:22,986 --> 00:00:28,976
♪Remembering the old days in a trance♪

2
00:00:29,326 --> 00:00:36,136
♪We are destined to fight together♪

3
00:00:36,416 --> 00:00:43,116
♪The past has gone but the memory lasts♪

4
00:00:43,436 --> 00:00:50,456
♪Our happiness and sorrow
in the good old days♪

5
00:00:50,666 --> 00:00:57,296
♪The journey is difficult,
through the crowds, to the end of time♪

6
00:00:57,616 --> 00:01:05,816
♪I'm brave and undefeatable♪

7
00:01:06,536 --> 00:01:13,566
♪The sky has become dark
and the birds have returned home♪

8
00:01:13,726 --> 00:01:20,776
♪Breaking all obstacles
and reaching the peak above the clouds♪

9
00:01:20,926 --> 00:01:27,776
♪Watching the thin plumes of smoke
and the beautiful scenery♪

10
00:01:27,936 --> 00:01:31,246
♪Working together,
overcoming all difficulties♪

11
00:01:31,516 --> 00:01:35,676
♪I will be known as the fearless one♪

12
00:01:35,676 --> 00:01:39,796
=Douluo Continent=

13
00:01:39,876 --> 00:01:42,836
=Episode 21=

14
00:01:42,879 --> 00:01:43,440
Never mind.

15
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:46,639
Our priority on this trip is still Dai Mu Bai.

16
00:01:47,279 --> 00:01:48,400
He shouldn't be a problem.

17
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:50,080
I think he was tempted just now.

18
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:55,120
What did Tang San tell you?

19
00:01:59,199 --> 00:02:00,959
Do you know Ye Zhi Qiu
from Cang Hui School?

20
00:02:01,599 --> 00:02:02,919
Never heard of it.

21
00:02:03,599 --> 00:02:04,400
Cang Hui?

22
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,680
It's a little unknown school.

23
00:02:07,440 --> 00:02:08,000
What's wrong?

24
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:11,239
Nothing.

25
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,800
Did Cang Hui School get ahead of us?

26
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:16,240
They came to Shi Lan Ke to recruit talents?

27
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:18,000
A petty school like that

28
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,440
is no match for us.

29
00:02:24,399 --> 00:02:25,080
Yu Tian Heng.

30
00:02:28,119 --> 00:02:28,759
Have you made up your mind?

31
00:02:29,399 --> 00:02:30,039
You mentioned

32
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:31,800
that as long as I joined
Tian Dou Imperial School,

33
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,360
your people would side with me

34
00:02:33,679 --> 00:02:34,720
in the conflict against my elder brother.

35
00:02:35,039 --> 00:02:37,399
Yes, Tian Dou Imperial School promises you.

36
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:40,759
What's so funny?

37
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:43,080
If I fight my brother,

38
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:45,360
it means the power struggle
between the heirs of Xin Luo Empire.

39
00:02:45,919 --> 00:02:47,960
How can a school have the authority
to support me?

40
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:50,639
So this promise

41
00:02:50,919 --> 00:02:52,080
didn't come from the school.

42
00:02:52,399 --> 00:02:53,000
Am I right?

43
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:57,399
You didn't dare to even tell the truth.

44
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:59,800
Tang San's decision will be mine as well.

45
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:00,800
Hold on.

46
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:06,160
Fine, you're right.

47
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:06,919
Captain.

48
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:08,559
Never mind, we can tell him.

49
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:11,279
Dai Mu Bai, someone wants to see you.

50
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:13,320
If you agree to join
Tian Dou Imperial School,

51
00:03:13,919 --> 00:03:15,559
in the future, in the power struggle
of Xing Luo Empire,

52
00:03:16,199 --> 00:03:18,199
you will have full support
from Tian Dou Empire.

53
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:19,600
Even if you need military support,

54
00:03:20,399 --> 00:03:21,440
we can provide it.

55
00:03:22,119 --> 00:03:23,759
So the tournament and the school

56
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,320
are only the pretext to use me

57
00:03:25,559 --> 00:03:26,600
to interfere with the power struggle
of Xing Luo Empire.

58
00:03:26,919 --> 00:03:28,720
No, don't think that way. It's too extreme.

59
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,440
We truly want to help you.

60
00:03:30,759 --> 00:03:31,360
"We"?

61
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,279
Who actually wants to help me?

62
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:35,759
It's Xue Qing He.

63
00:03:37,839 --> 00:03:38,839
Who is that?

64
00:03:40,279 --> 00:03:41,639
The only heir to the throne
of Tian Dou Empire.

65
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:43,440
Xue Qing He, the Crown Prince.

66
00:03:44,039 --> 00:03:45,160
The sudden announcement of the contest

67
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,080
shocked the entire Douluo Continent.

68
00:03:46,559 --> 00:03:48,520
Every Soul Master School is preparing for it.

69
00:03:49,039 --> 00:03:50,520
But Xue Qing He thinks

70
00:03:51,119 --> 00:03:53,520
there is a conspiracy behind the contest.

71
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:54,800
What conspiracy?

72
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,199
I have no idea either.

73
00:03:56,679 --> 00:03:57,839
You may ask him yourself.

74
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,279
Why didn't he come to see me?

75
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:00,600
His Highness thinks

76
00:04:00,880 --> 00:04:02,240
too many parties are involved in this case.

77
00:04:02,839 --> 00:04:03,919
Besides, the inside of Tian Dou City

78
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,440
isn't as peaceful as it seems.

79
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,240
He can only meet you in private.

80
00:04:07,759 --> 00:04:09,559
So the proposal to recruit us

81
00:04:09,679 --> 00:04:10,440
was false?

82
00:04:10,759 --> 00:04:12,960
No. We are indeed
recruiting new members.

83
00:04:13,679 --> 00:04:14,720
That's all I know.

84
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:15,919
For more details,

85
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:17,880
you may ask the Crown Prince.

86
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:23,079
Yan Zi, what's wrong?

87
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:29,839
I think she's been poisoned.

88
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:31,720
Poisoned? How is that possible?

89
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,000
We've been travelling together.

90
00:04:33,239 --> 00:04:35,000
Why wasn't I poisoned?

91
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:41,359
She needs to eat this now.

92
00:04:41,359 --> 00:04:42,320
It'll cure her.

93
00:04:44,359 --> 00:04:46,559
Weeping Forsythia.
I've never seen this before.

94
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,200
This is my Second Soul Skill.

95
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:49,640
Vitalizing Weeping Forsythia.

96
00:04:50,239 --> 00:04:51,239
Try it out, it's delicious.

97
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,040
No. I'm afraid it's bitter.

98
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:54,480
It's not bitter at all.

99
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:55,799
It can even cure poison.

100
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:01,040
She is awake!

101
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:01,880
See? She's awake!

102
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:06,920
What happened to me just now?

103
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:09,200
Where are we?

104
00:05:10,519 --> 00:05:11,519
He said you had been poisoned.

105
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:12,279
Poisoned?

106
00:05:13,679 --> 00:05:14,600
Why don't I remember that?

107
00:05:14,679 --> 00:05:16,000
It's all right. You are cured.

108
00:05:20,799 --> 00:05:22,160
This can't be right!

109
00:05:22,279 --> 00:05:23,480
My Weeping Forsythia

110
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,440
cures everything!

111
00:05:24,799 --> 00:05:26,359
Maybe you should have another one.

112
00:05:27,279 --> 00:05:29,079
I doubt the capability of your Martial Soul.

113
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:31,239
Maybe she fainted because of hunger.

114
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:32,959
I have some sausages.

115
00:05:32,959 --> 00:05:33,480
Do you want some?

116
00:05:35,519 --> 00:05:36,640
Maybe we should get a doctor.

117
00:05:39,279 --> 00:05:39,760
Never mind.

118
00:05:40,359 --> 00:05:41,279
Du Gu Yan's identity is special.

119
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:42,839
I'm taking her back to Tian Dou City.

120
00:05:43,279 --> 00:05:44,040
If she has been poisoned,

121
00:05:44,359 --> 00:05:45,559
her elder will definitely handle it.

122
00:05:46,399 --> 00:05:47,760
I was supposed to go with you,

123
00:05:48,079 --> 00:05:49,880
but under the circumstances, I must go now.

124
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,480
You two depart later.

125
00:05:51,559 --> 00:05:53,880
Make it to Xi Si City in ten days
to meet His Highness.

126
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:55,320
His Highness?

127
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:56,279
Xi Si City?

128
00:05:56,679 --> 00:05:57,239
What is it?

129
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:00,959
Xi Si City Soul Arena.

130
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,040
Accept the Fiend Battle Team's challenge.

131
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,079
Once you overcome the challenge,

132
00:06:05,440 --> 00:06:06,880
you're qualified to go to Cang Hui School

133
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,200
in Tian Dou City and see me.

134
00:06:08,559 --> 00:06:09,959
Why are we meeting in Xi Si City?

135
00:06:10,279 --> 00:06:11,959
The meeting between His Highness
and Dai Mu Bai is a top secret.

136
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:12,760
First of all,

137
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:14,799
Xi Si City is on the way to the Capital.

138
00:06:15,279 --> 00:06:15,839
Secondly,

139
00:06:16,079 --> 00:06:17,079
there is no Governor in that city.

140
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,359
The city is not owned by anyone.

141
00:06:18,799 --> 00:06:21,079
The place will provide more cover.

142
00:06:21,959 --> 00:06:22,519
Remember

143
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:24,799
to reach Xi Si City in ten days
to meet His Highness.

144
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:37,519
Rong Rong, where is Wu?

145
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:38,839
Her legs haven't fully recovered.

146
00:06:38,839 --> 00:06:39,839
Sister Qing is looking after her.

147
00:06:40,959 --> 00:06:41,640
Do you know

148
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:43,600
why Headmaster wants us to come here?

149
00:06:43,839 --> 00:06:44,640
I have no idea.

150
00:06:45,079 --> 00:06:45,600
I don't know.

151
00:06:46,839 --> 00:06:48,239
What are we going to do here?

152
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,359
Why is she still here?

153
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,679
She was hurt in the fight
against Dai Wei Shi.

154
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,119
I couldn't just kick her out.

155
00:06:56,839 --> 00:06:57,640
Should we avoid her?

156
00:06:59,239 --> 00:07:00,359
She will find it out sooner or later.

157
00:07:02,559 --> 00:07:03,279
Where is Yu Tian Heng?

158
00:07:04,079 --> 00:07:04,760
He left.

159
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:07,440
I'll get to the point.

160
00:07:07,679 --> 00:07:08,880
Do not mention Xue Qing He.

161
00:07:10,399 --> 00:07:11,760
Martial Soul Hall is organizing

162
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:13,720
the Soul Master School Contest.

163
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,279
Tian Dou Imperial School

164
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,959
formally invited Tang San and Dai Mu Bai

165
00:07:16,959 --> 00:07:18,160
to join their team

166
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,079
in the contest.

167
00:07:19,559 --> 00:07:20,000
Not bad!

168
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:20,799
Impressive, Brother San.

169
00:07:21,239 --> 00:07:22,279
Even Tian Dou Imperial School knows him.

170
00:07:24,239 --> 00:07:25,440
After much consideration,

171
00:07:26,959 --> 00:07:28,399
we've decided to let you

172
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:30,519
go to Tian Dou City

173
00:07:30,799 --> 00:07:32,279
and participate in this event.

174
00:07:32,839 --> 00:07:33,760
But Headmaster,

175
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:35,279
joining Tian Dou Imperial School

176
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:36,760
means quitting Shi Lan Ke School.

177
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:39,320
The goal of Shi Lan Ke School

178
00:07:39,399 --> 00:07:40,920
is to train up the best Soul Masters.

179
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:42,359
The best Soul Master

180
00:07:42,359 --> 00:07:44,359
needs to hone his skills and face challenges

181
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:45,480
to make progress.

182
00:07:46,399 --> 00:07:47,480
Martial Soul Hall

183
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:49,000
is providing the greatest platform,

184
00:07:49,079 --> 00:07:50,480
and as your headmaster,

185
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,640
I must show you the world.

186
00:07:54,359 --> 00:07:55,000
But Headmaster...

187
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:55,679
I know.

188
00:07:56,399 --> 00:07:57,000
I also hope

189
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,480
you guys will always be the students
of Shi Lan Ke.

190
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,200
But I can't force you to give up

191
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:01,519
this great chance

192
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,239
just to keep you in Shi Lan Ke.

193
00:08:03,799 --> 00:08:04,959
Wouldn't that be too selfish of me

194
00:08:04,959 --> 00:08:06,239
to do such a thing?

195
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,160
So,

196
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,440
not only Tang San and Dai Mu Bai are going there,

197
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,799
all members of our school

198
00:08:12,279 --> 00:08:13,359
will go to the Capital together!

199
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:15,399
-Really?
-It's real?

200
00:08:16,959 --> 00:08:18,640
You should see for yourselves

201
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:19,880
how many geniuses there are

202
00:08:19,880 --> 00:08:21,000
in Douluo Continent.

203
00:08:21,799 --> 00:08:23,559
Get ready, everyone.

204
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:24,760
We'll set out tomorrow morning.

205
00:08:25,239 --> 00:08:25,519
Yes!

206
00:08:25,519 --> 00:08:26,239
This is great!

207
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:27,279
If we go to the Capital,

208
00:08:27,359 --> 00:08:28,679
I might get to meet my father.

209
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:29,799
I must tell

210
00:08:29,799 --> 00:08:30,920
Wu and Sister Qing now.

211
00:08:32,160 --> 00:08:32,679
Master.

212
00:08:36,160 --> 00:08:36,720
He said

213
00:08:37,079 --> 00:08:38,000
that the school

214
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,320
shouldn't become the shackles
that bind you.

215
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:41,359
If it can give you a brighter future,

216
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:43,320
even with the school as your stepping stone,

217
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,239
he must let you fly high.

218
00:08:45,799 --> 00:08:47,559
Even if he loses all the students,

219
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,159
it is worth it.

220
00:08:50,359 --> 00:08:51,559
I'm not leaving Shi Lan Ke.

221
00:08:52,679 --> 00:08:53,280
I won't either.

222
00:08:54,640 --> 00:08:56,000
Set out with that belief.

223
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:57,400
This is an eye-opener

224
00:08:57,719 --> 00:08:59,200
that will let you grow.

225
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:02,760
I wish we could participate

226
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:03,320
as the students of Shi Lan Ke School.

227
00:09:04,559 --> 00:09:06,679
There might be other opportunities
in Tian Dou City.

228
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:10,200
I'll go to pack things up.

229
00:09:16,599 --> 00:09:17,119
Headmaster.

230
00:09:24,159 --> 00:09:25,679
Are you really taking them
to Tian Dou City?

231
00:09:26,559 --> 00:09:28,200
Do you want to get in my way?

232
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:29,280
No.

233
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,520
I'm going back to the Capital.

234
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:32,520
We are going in the same direction.

235
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:34,679
You will travel faster without us.

236
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:36,239
I'm not in a hurry.

237
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:40,520
You haven't given up on Dai Mu Bai?

238
00:09:41,520 --> 00:09:43,400
I won't quit so easily.

239
00:09:44,119 --> 00:09:45,880
I know what you did to Dai Mu Bai.

240
00:09:48,119 --> 00:09:49,799
If you try to harm my students again,

241
00:09:50,719 --> 00:09:52,080
I will stop you.

242
00:10:09,359 --> 00:10:09,760
Master.

243
00:10:10,559 --> 00:10:11,320
We'll pass by Xi Si City

244
00:10:12,039 --> 00:10:13,000
on our journey.

245
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:17,880
Are you still thinking
about challenging the Fiend Battle Team?

246
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:22,039
Master, I want to find my father.

247
00:10:22,359 --> 00:10:23,760
I want to know what he's doing.

248
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,239
I want to know what happened to him.

249
00:10:28,359 --> 00:10:30,039
This is probably my only chance.

250
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:36,039
Very well.

251
00:10:36,679 --> 00:10:37,919
I'll inform Lander,

252
00:10:38,679 --> 00:10:40,039
so he won't stop you then.

253
00:10:41,760 --> 00:10:42,559
Thank you, Master.

254
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:44,200
By the way,

255
00:10:44,559 --> 00:10:47,000
don't tell the others about my plan.

256
00:10:48,479 --> 00:10:50,520
What about Wu? Won't you tell her?

257
00:10:51,039 --> 00:10:52,000
I don't want her to be worried.

258
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:43,320
I wish I could

259
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,239
take everything about the school with me.

260
00:11:53,359 --> 00:11:53,919
Come on.

261
00:12:23,649 --> 00:12:25,690
♪The twilight shows up at daybreak♪

262
00:12:26,330 --> 00:12:28,209
♪The youth rides a horse♪

263
00:12:28,490 --> 00:12:30,649
♪When the world turns around♪

264
00:12:30,930 --> 00:12:34,209
♪The sky is reflected in the eyes♪

265
00:12:34,769 --> 00:12:36,930
♪Overcome the trial in abyss♪

266
00:12:37,570 --> 00:12:39,570
♪Yet remain unchanged♪

267
00:12:39,690 --> 00:12:41,810
♪Walking upright in the world♪

268
00:12:42,130 --> 00:12:44,289
♪The breeze in spring is tender♪

269
00:12:44,609 --> 00:12:49,649
♪Have the belief to save the day♪

270
00:12:50,130 --> 00:12:56,609
♪Go on a great adventure♪

271
00:12:58,490 --> 00:13:01,010
♪Join hands and look at the world♪

272
00:13:01,649 --> 00:13:03,249
♪Overlook the sky♪

273
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:04,200
Wait!

274
00:14:31,010 --> 00:14:33,529
♪Join hands and look at the world♪

275
00:14:34,169 --> 00:14:36,529
♪Overlook the sky♪

276
00:14:36,890 --> 00:14:39,370
♪The light is so brilliant♪

277
00:14:39,370 --> 00:14:42,050
♪The dream is burning in my chest♪

