399
00:21:41,119 --> 00:21:41,880
Why?

400
00:21:42,079 --> 00:21:44,040
The merchant is their owner.

401
00:21:44,040 --> 00:21:44,560
That's right.

402
00:21:44,800 --> 00:21:46,640
Their relationship is equal and cooperative.

403
00:21:47,280 --> 00:21:49,040
The merchant will attract the customers,

404
00:21:49,280 --> 00:21:51,560
and the Sand Beasts contribute their talent.

405
00:21:52,199 --> 00:21:54,000
Talent? What talent?

406
00:21:54,199 --> 00:21:54,760
Silly.

407
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:58,160
Their talent is being cute, of course.

408
00:21:59,199 --> 00:22:00,880
How is being cute a talent?

409
00:22:01,160 --> 00:22:02,199
In that case,

410
00:22:02,400 --> 00:22:03,280
I'm also cute.

411
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:04,199
I am talented.

412
00:22:04,199 --> 00:22:04,880
I am interesting.

413
00:22:04,959 --> 00:22:05,599
Isn't that right?

414
00:22:06,920 --> 00:22:09,119
So how do they split the profit?

415
00:22:09,319 --> 00:22:10,920
All the money goes to the Sand Beasts.

416
00:22:11,400 --> 00:22:12,359
All the money?

417
00:22:12,359 --> 00:22:13,560
The Sand Beasts use money?

418
00:22:14,280 --> 00:22:15,839
Do not underestimate
the intelligence of Soul Beasts.

419
00:22:16,439 --> 00:22:18,359
A full-grown Sand Beast

420
00:22:18,359 --> 00:22:19,959
has the intelligence of a child.

421
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:23,719
The merchant will send the food
out of the city for them

422
00:22:23,719 --> 00:22:25,000
to the Sand Beast herd.

423
00:22:27,719 --> 00:22:28,839
That means

424
00:22:29,079 --> 00:22:30,680
the Sand Beasts are social animals.

425
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:33,839
The merchant delivers food for them

426
00:22:33,839 --> 00:22:34,839
