430
00:22:39,520 --> 00:22:40,880
when he crosses the desert.

431
00:22:42,040 --> 00:22:43,359
Protection?

432
00:22:43,880 --> 00:22:46,520
But they look so adorable.

433
00:22:47,119 --> 00:22:48,520
