439
00:22:59,400 --> 00:22:59,959
Actually,

440
00:22:59,959 --> 00:23:02,479
Sand Beasts have the ability
to control sandstorm.

441
00:23:03,119 --> 00:23:04,199
When they feel threatened,

442
00:23:04,680 --> 00:23:07,119
the Sand Beasts are capable of destroying a city.

443
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:10,680
They are invincible in the desert.

444
00:23:11,239 --> 00:23:13,680
But the Sand Beasts are friendly and tame.

445
00:23:13,920 --> 00:23:15,839
