for the humans.

446
00:23:15,959 --> 00:23:17,040
Then a mutual relationship

447
00:23:17,040 --> 00:23:18,400
started to form between humans and Sand Beasts.

448
00:23:18,479 --> 00:23:19,400
I see.

449
00:23:19,439 --> 00:23:21,640
Humans and Soul Beasts
can live in harmony.

450
00:23:22,520 --> 00:23:23,119
Of course.

451
00:23:23,880 --> 00:23:25,000
In that case,

452
00:23:26,400 --> 00:23:29,040
if all the Soul Beasts could
form a mutual relationship with us,

453
00:23:29,760 --> 00:23:31,880
there would be no more hunting!

454
00:23:32,479 --> 00:23:33,199
Am I right?

455
00:23:33,319 --> 00:23:34,160
This is only an exception.

456
00:23:34,599 --> 00:23:37,000
As long as Soul Masters still need
to hunt down Soul Beasts

457
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:37,839
to advance their Soul Rings,

458
00:23:38,439 --> 00:23:39,040
humans and Soul Beasts

459
00:23:39,040 --> 00:23:41,000
