560
00:28:08,199 --> 00:28:09,560
What's wrong with the Fiend Battle Team?

561
00:28:09,640 --> 00:28:10,599
In the Soul Arena,

562
00:28:10,839 --> 00:28:13,040
those who fought the Fiend Battle Team

563
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:15,280
have mostly died.

564
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:17,959
Those who survived were tied up

565
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:19,160
and left in the sun outside the city.

566
00:28:23,359 --> 00:28:24,680
What happened?

567
00:28:27,239 --> 00:28:28,719
The Fiend Battle Team did that?

568
00:28:29,760 --> 00:28:31,319
If they are so brutal,

569
00:28:31,959 --> 00:28:33,520
why would the Soul Masters want to fight them?

570
00:28:33,959 --> 00:28:35,040
Their families were captured.

571
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:37,880
If they don't fight,
they will lose their entire families.

572
00:28:37,959 --> 00:28:38,719
Where is the authority?

573
00:28:39,959 --> 00:28:41,920
Xi Si City has no Governor.

574
00:28:42,280 --> 00:28:44,040
The city is in anarchy.

575
00:28:44,680 --> 00:28:45,439
In this city,

576
00:28:46,479 --> 00:28:48,079
it's the survival of the fittest.

577
00:28:49,719 --> 00:28:51,599
Is the Fiend Battle Team very strong?

578
00:28:52,079 --> 00:28:55,319
They are almost all
Quadruple Soul Rings Soul Sects.

579
00:28:55,640 --> 00:28:56,560
What do you think?

580
00:28:56,800 --> 00:28:59,079
Quadruple Soul Rings? And more than one?

581
00:29:28,640 --> 00:29:30,800
Tang San? Wu?

582
00:29:31,839 --> 00:29:32,520
Wang Sheng.

583
00:29:44,959 --> 00:29:45,599
Who are you?

584
00:29:46,439 --> 00:29:47,839
Young Master, what's wrong?

585
00:29:53,599 --> 00:29:55,280
Tell them you're all right.

586
00:29:56,479 --> 00:29:57,280
I'm all right.

587
00:29:58,520 --> 00:29:59,959
Where is Xue Qing He?

588
00:30:00,839 --> 00:30:02,040
His Highness is in Tian Dou City.

589
00:30:04,680 --> 00:30:06,280
Why doesn't he come to Xi Si City?

590
00:30:09,119 --> 00:30:10,160
He planned to come here.

591
00:30:11,160 --> 00:30:13,439
But the Prince wanted to
have a word with His Highness.

592
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:14,920
He couldn't make it in time.

593
00:30:16,040 --> 00:30:17,359
In Tian Dou City,

594
00:30:17,359 --> 00:30:19,680
will he look for Dai Mu Bai?

595
00:30:20,439 --> 00:30:22,359
Sure, certainly.

596
00:30:22,839 --> 00:30:26,280
Why does Xue Qing He want to meet Dai Mu Bai?

597
00:30:26,680 --> 00:30:27,359
I don't know.

598
00:30:34,439 --> 00:30:35,680
Why is the robe on the floor?

599
00:30:40,319 --> 00:30:42,239
Young Master, I was shocked.

600
00:30:42,319 --> 00:30:43,000
What happened?

601
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:44,400
I heard you yell.

602
00:30:44,719 --> 00:30:45,719
I didn't yell.

603
00:30:46,800 --> 00:30:47,280
Let's go.

604
00:30:47,640 --> 00:30:48,880
If I keep staying in the inn,

605
00:30:49,359 --> 00:30:50,719
I won't have time to check out the city.

606
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:52,000
I heard there are many specialties.

607
00:30:52,800 --> 00:30:53,839
I could buy them as souvenirs.

608
00:30:57,599 --> 00:30:58,439
What is it, Young Master?

609
00:30:58,760 --> 00:30:59,439
That girl...

610
00:31:00,319 --> 00:31:01,359
She looks familiar.

611
00:31:04,079 --> 00:31:05,119
Forget it, let's go.

612
00:31:05,359 --> 00:31:06,000
I might be mistaken.

613
00:31:18,959 --> 00:31:20,839
I feel like our days in Nuoding School

614
00:31:22,040 --> 00:31:23,040
were merely yesterday.

615
00:31:24,599 --> 00:31:25,760
Time flies.

616
00:31:26,520 --> 00:31:28,680
Back then, the attached students
were like a family.

617
00:31:29,119 --> 00:31:30,599
We took part in the election
of the Soul Master Association.

618
00:31:30,920 --> 00:31:31,719
We went to class together.

619
00:31:32,040 --> 00:31:32,680
It was a pleasant time.

620
00:31:34,319 --> 00:31:36,119
Wang Sheng, what are you doing here?

621
00:31:36,839 --> 00:31:37,479
I escaped here.

622
00:31:38,040 --> 00:31:38,800
Why did you escape?

623
00:31:41,000 --> 00:31:42,680
I've been keeping something from you.

624
00:31:43,239 --> 00:31:43,920
I feel guilty.

625
00:31:44,400 --> 00:31:46,079
Do you remember Xiao Chen Yu?

626
00:31:46,439 --> 00:31:47,199
Sure.

627
00:31:47,520 --> 00:31:49,000
He captured me with a cage.

628
00:31:49,319 --> 00:31:51,079
Luckily, Tang San saved me.

629
00:31:51,560 --> 00:31:54,119
Actually, I killed Xiao Chen Yu.

630
00:31:57,560 --> 00:31:58,920
I'm going to kill you!

631
00:32:01,719 --> 00:32:02,800
After I escaped,

632
00:32:03,119 --> 00:32:05,560
I found that they framed you as the killer.

633
00:32:06,760 --> 00:32:08,880
I feel sorry for letting you take the blame.

634
00:32:09,400 --> 00:32:10,319
Why did you kill him?

635
00:32:11,479 --> 00:32:12,920
He made me betray you.

636
00:32:13,359 --> 00:32:14,719
He even wanted to kill me.

637
00:32:15,479 --> 00:32:16,560
Since I had the opportunity,

638
00:32:17,319 --> 00:32:18,560
I wouldn't let them get away.

639
00:32:19,479 --> 00:32:20,599
I must take revenge on them

640
00:32:20,800 --> 00:32:21,719
for what I went through.

641
00:32:22,239 --> 00:32:23,000
He deserved to die.

642
00:32:25,239 --> 00:32:27,040
Actually, our fellow students

643
00:32:27,319 --> 00:32:28,239
are true friends.

644
00:32:29,199 --> 00:32:30,000
Did you just arrive today?

645
00:32:30,880 --> 00:32:31,199
Yes.

646
00:32:31,839 --> 00:32:32,680
Have you been to the market?

647
00:32:33,400 --> 00:32:33,880
Yes.

648
00:32:34,319 --> 00:32:35,040
What did you buy?

649
00:32:35,839 --> 00:32:36,479
Nothing.

650
00:32:37,800 --> 00:32:38,599
Nothing interested you?

651
00:32:41,959 --> 00:32:42,560
There is.

652
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:44,680
I like that candy.

653
00:32:44,800 --> 00:32:45,479
The candy?

654
00:32:45,760 --> 00:32:46,880
Come with me.

655
00:32:55,359 --> 00:32:55,800
Here you go.

656
00:32:56,640 --> 00:32:58,119
Is this your shop?

657
00:32:58,760 --> 00:33:00,040
I don't have the time.

658
00:33:00,560 --> 00:33:01,640
Why didn't you pay?

659
00:33:03,479 --> 00:33:04,319
In this city,

660
00:33:04,640 --> 00:33:05,439
if you want something,

661
00:33:05,760 --> 00:33:06,560
just let me know.

662
00:33:06,959 --> 00:33:07,520
I can get it for free.

663
00:33:09,560 --> 00:33:10,079
Wang Sheng.

664
00:33:11,280 --> 00:33:12,599
I think they are afraid of you.

665
00:33:14,959 --> 00:33:16,920
The weak fears the strong.

666
00:33:18,160 --> 00:33:18,599
Take it.

667
00:33:19,920 --> 00:33:20,719
I can't take this.

668
00:33:21,880 --> 00:33:22,520
Why not?

669
00:33:23,439 --> 00:33:25,199
If you don't pay for it, it's robbing.

670
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:26,920
I don't want that candy.

671
00:33:34,880 --> 00:33:35,760
Since you've arrived,

672
00:33:36,160 --> 00:33:37,119
why didn't you come to us?

673
00:33:37,599 --> 00:33:38,359
"Us"?

674
00:33:39,479 --> 00:33:40,319
Didn't Master Ye

675
00:33:40,520 --> 00:33:41,439
tell you?

676
00:33:41,800 --> 00:33:43,800
You should come to us
when you arrived in Xi Si City.

677
00:33:44,160 --> 00:33:45,520
You know Ye Zhi Qiu too?

678
00:33:46,319 --> 00:33:48,319
Why should we go to you?

679
00:33:48,439 --> 00:33:50,439
Wu, it's getting late.

680
00:33:50,719 --> 00:33:51,599
Let me walk you back.

681
00:33:51,959 --> 00:33:53,160
But...

682
00:33:57,359 --> 00:33:58,760
There is nothing funny.

683
00:33:59,319 --> 00:34:01,359
You can't compare this place
with Tian Dou City.

684
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:05,079
What is this?

685
00:34:05,599 --> 00:34:06,599
It looks funny.

686
00:34:07,560 --> 00:34:08,760
We've never been to Xi Si City before.

687
00:34:09,439 --> 00:34:10,920
Maybe they are beasts that pull carriages.

688
00:34:12,079 --> 00:34:12,800
They are ugly yet cute.

689
00:34:13,239 --> 00:34:14,280
They look interesting.

690
00:34:16,080 --> 00:34:17,479
So you are on the Fiend Battle Team.

691
00:34:19,439 --> 00:34:19,959
Yes.

692
00:34:20,600 --> 00:34:21,919
I'm one of their members.

693
00:34:23,040 --> 00:34:24,040
After I left Nuoding City,

694
00:34:24,840 --> 00:34:27,120
I wanted to attend another Soul Master School.

695
00:34:28,520 --> 00:34:30,439
But I couldn't afford the fees.

696
00:34:31,719 --> 00:34:32,919
Then I considered going to Martial Soul Hall.

697
00:34:33,439 --> 00:34:34,719
But the people there

698
00:34:35,399 --> 00:34:36,639
looked down on me.

699
00:34:38,520 --> 00:34:41,040
They said I wasn't gifted and wouldn't take me in.

700
00:34:42,159 --> 00:34:42,639
Then,

701
00:34:42,919 --> 00:34:44,439
I wandered from city to city.

702
00:34:44,919 --> 00:34:45,959
I ran out of money soon.

703
00:34:47,199 --> 00:34:48,120
Later, I found

704
00:34:48,600 --> 00:34:50,399
that some cities would open up

705
00:34:50,840 --> 00:34:52,360
some underground Soul Arenas.

706
00:34:53,199 --> 00:34:54,760
The Soul Masters would fight there.

707
00:34:55,639 --> 00:34:56,280
You kill or get killed.

708
00:34:57,239 --> 00:34:58,120
Though it's dangerous,

709
00:34:58,679 --> 00:35:00,439
you can make a fortune if you win.

710
00:35:01,280 --> 00:35:02,120
So I joined.

711
00:35:03,199 --> 00:35:05,879
But I completely lost at the first time.

712
00:35:07,120 --> 00:35:08,280
I was about to be killed.

713
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:10,479
Do you know what happened next?

714
00:35:11,560 --> 00:35:12,120
I can't guess.

715
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:14,919
My Martial Soul mutated.

716
00:35:29,679 --> 00:35:31,479
My ordinary Tiger Soul

717
00:35:31,959 --> 00:35:32,719
turned into a Blood Tiger Soul.

718
00:35:33,479 --> 00:35:34,919
God gave me a chance!

719
00:35:36,360 --> 00:35:37,159
After the mutation,

720
00:35:37,600 --> 00:35:39,399
the force behind the Fiend Battle Team found me.

721
00:35:39,719 --> 00:35:40,280
They told me

722
00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:42,959
that whoever works alone will be bullied.

723
00:35:43,120 --> 00:35:44,159
But if we stick together,

724
00:35:44,719 --> 00:35:45,479
it will be different.

725
00:36:13,200 --> 00:36:17,960
♪The trees are shining
against the light♪

726
00:36:18,600 --> 00:36:23,720
♪Like a stubborn young man♪

727
00:36:24,520 --> 00:36:29,660
♪The far destination is
where I'm heading♪

728
00:36:29,900 --> 00:36:36,110
♪My bags are packed but I'm in a daze♪

729
00:36:36,480 --> 00:36:41,640
♪There's no need to comfort me♪

730
00:36:42,090 --> 00:36:47,600
♪Going separate ways
and we'll all endure suffering♪

731
00:36:47,950 --> 00:36:53,390
♪Don't hide,
take it as another challenge for us♪

732
00:36:53,760 --> 00:37:00,350
♪A stubborn choice and a burning heart♪

733
00:37:00,680 --> 00:37:03,600
♪Take the bumpy road under the storm♪

734
00:37:03,680 --> 00:37:06,350
♪Not afraid to
break ordinary rules in life♪

735
00:37:06,510 --> 00:37:07,800
♪Because♪

736
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:12,430
♪Because I want to
become the unique one♪

737
